        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Vidhwa Vivah Uphar Yojana is a government Under the Social Justice and Empowerment Department, scheme that assists in the process of marriage of widows. This scheme is for those widows who have decided to start a new life after the time spent with their former husbands. The government provides a certain amount to widows, which can be used in the marriage of widows. The money is used to help widows meet the comfortable needs of their new home.\n",
        "benefits_md": "> Financial Assistance/Gift amount ₹51,000/-\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The Rajasthan government's Social Justice and Empowerment Department launched the \"Vidhva Vivah Uphar Yojana\" program, a social welfare initiative that aims to improve the lives of widow women. ",
        "exclusions_md": "",
